-- House Prices in South Africa Rose 1% in January From Year Ago, Absa Says
-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 2011-02-07T06:05:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-07/house-prices-in-south-africa-rose-1-in-january-from-year-ago-absa-says.html
The average price of a medium-sized
house in  South Africa  increased by 1 percent in January from a
year earlier,  Absa Group Ltd . said in an e-mailed statement
today from Johannesburg.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
